782
01:01:38,111 --> 01:01:40,524
Well, we thought you was
coming with Gino, Lucy.

783
01:01:40,739 --> 01:01:42,605
Jill, do you wanna dance?

784
01:01:43,325 --> 01:01:46,693
Oh, you kids go ahead and
