785
01:01:46,786 --> 01:01:49,699
- Lucy, Lucy, dance with me!
- No! No!

786
01:01:58,882 --> 01:02:00,714
Get out of it!

787
01:02:21,571 --> 01:02:22,857
Hey, remember me?

788
01:02:31,706 --> 01:02:33,447
Having fun?

789
01:02:35,001 --> 01:02:36,367
Yeah, fine, and you?

790
01:02:36,461 --> 01:02:39,329
So so. There's a big brute
