873
01:06:16,931 --> 01:06:19,639
Hey Tom, Scottie, Johnny.
Come on!

874
01:06:21,144 --> 01:06:22,931
- Yeah.
- Now then, Red, no trouble.

875
01:06:22,937 --> 01:06:24,098
No trouble, please.

876
01:06:40,997 --> 01:06:43,455
